rectangle "wsession command" as wsession_cmd
usecase "list subcommand" as wsession_list
usecase "show subcommand" as wsession_show
usecase "tree subcommand" as wsession_tree
usecase "breadcrumbs subcommand" as wsession_breadcrumbs
usecase "timeline subcommand" as wsession_timeline
usecase "stats subcommand" as wsession_stats
wsession_cmd --> wsession_list
wsession_cmd --> wsession_show
wsession_cmd --> wsession_tree
wsession_cmd --> wsession_breadcrumbs
wsession_cmd --> wsession_timeline
wsession_cmd --> wsession_stats

note left of NOTE_ANCHOR
  **Evidence:**
  * [[v1/command_surface/cmd_wsession.md cmd_wsession.md]]
